'''埃塞俄比亞復興大壩'''（{{lang-am|ታላቁ የኢትዮጵያ ሕዳሴ ግድብ|translit=Tālāqu ye-Ītyōppyā Hidāsē Gidib }}）是[[埃塞俄比亞|埃塞俄比亞]]境內[[青尼罗河|青尼罗河]]一條[[重力壩|重力壩]]，位於[[本尚古勒-古馬茲州|本尚古勒-古馬茲州]]，鄰近蘇丹邊境。<ref>{{cite web|title=Ethiopia’s biggest dam to help neighbours solve power problem|url=http://www.inewsone.com/2011/04/17/ethiopias-biggest-dam-to-help-neighbours-solve-power-problem/43904|accessdate=2011-04-17|date=2011-04-17|publisher=News One|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120322030951/http://www.inewsone.com/2011/04/17/ethiopias-biggest-dam-to-help-neighbours-solve-power-problem/43904|archivedate=2012年3月22日|deadurl=yes}}</ref>該壩完工後的裝機容量可達6,000[[兆瓦|兆瓦]]，將會是非洲最大的[[水力發電站|水力發電站]]。<ref>{{cite news|title=Ethiopia lays foundation for Africa’s biggest dam|url=http://www.ertagov.com/erta/erta-news-archive/38-erta-tv-hot-news-addis-ababa-ethiopia/574-ethiopia-lays-foundation-for-africas-biggest-dam.html|accessdate=2011-04-19|newspaper=ERTA News|date=2011-04-02|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110412060039/http://www.ertagov.com/erta/erta-news-archive/38-erta-tv-hot-news-addis-ababa-ethiopia/574-ethiopia-lays-foundation-for-africas-biggest-dam.html|archivedate=2011年4月12日}}</ref>大壩蓄水而成的水庫預計有630億立方米容量。<ref name="salini">{{cite web|title=Salini will build the biggest dam in Africa|url=http://www.salini.it/index.php/english/content/show_news/77|accessdate=2011-04-17|date=2011-03-31|publisher=Salini Construttori|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110430121639/http://www.salini.it/index.php/english/content/show_news/77|archive-date=2011-04-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>2020年7月该大坝已开始蓄水，预计蓄水完成需要5-15年。<ref name="bbcnews-celebrations">{{cite news|title=Nile dam row: Egypt fumes as Ethiopia celebrates|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-53573154|work=BBC News|date=2020-07-30|accessdate=2020-11-09|archive-date=2020-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201006083345/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-53573154|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="tractebel-20200910">{{cite web|title=Ethiopia: First stage of the filling of the reservoir of the Grand Renaissance Dam|url=https://tractebel-engie.com/en/news/2020/ethiopia-first-stage-of-the-filling-of-the-reservoir-of-the-grand-renaissance-dam|access-date=2020-10-27|date=2020-09-10|website=Tractebel Engie|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030234631/https://tractebel-engie.com/en/news/2020/ethiopia-first-stage-of-the-filling-of-the-reservoir-of-the-grand-renaissance-dam|archive-date=2020-10-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[苏丹共和国|蘇丹]]支持埃塞俄比亞興建大壩，不過反對由埃塞俄比亞單方面決定大壩的蓄水和運作。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.un.org/zh/story/2021/07/1087982|title=【专题报道】复兴大坝争端继续发酵 埃塞、埃及、苏丹在安理会较力|work=聯合國新聞|date=2021-07-14|accessdate=2021-07-17|archive-date=2021-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210719183443/https://news.un.org/zh/story/2021/07/1087982|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[尼羅河|尼羅河]]最下游的[[埃及|埃及]]擔心復興大壩會減少流入埃及的尼羅河水量。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-26679225|title=Will Ethiopia's Grand Renaissance Dam dry the Nile in Egypt?|work=BBC News|date=2014-03-22|accessdate=2015-03-24|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108193408/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-26679225|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年3月，三國領導人就建壩爭議達成初步協議。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-32016763|title=Egypt, Ethiopia and Sudan sign deal to end Nile dispute|work=BBC News|date=2015-03-23|accessdate=2015-03-24|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113114656/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-32016763|dead-url=no}}</ref>2018年1月，埃塞俄比亞總理[[海爾馬里亞姆·德薩萊尼|海爾馬里亞姆·德薩萊尼]]拒絕埃及提出由[[世界银行|世界银行]]進行[[仲裁|仲裁]]的提議。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2018-01/23/c_129796540.htm|title=尼罗河水权之争关乎生死 埃塞拒世界银行仲裁|publisher=新華網|date=2018-01-23|accessdate=2018-01-26|archive-date=2019-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190515085019/http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2018-01/23/c_129796540.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年7月26日，復興大壩的項目經理{{Link-en|西莫格努·貝克萊|Simegnew Bekele}}的屍體在埃塞俄比亞首都[[亚的斯亚贝巴|亚的斯亚贝巴]]被發現，死因是槍傷。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-44981490|title=Why Ethiopia is grieving for 'hero' dam engineer Simegnew Bekele|work=BBC News|date=2018-07-29|accessdate=2018-07-30|archive-date=2020-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921040952/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-44981490|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在衛星圖像顯示復興大壩水庫水位上升後，埃塞俄比亞水利、灌溉與能源部長西莱希·贝克莱於2020年7月15日向國營媒體EBC確認復興大壩開始蓄水。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-53416277|title=River Nile dam: Reservoir filling up, Ethiopia confirms|publisher=BBC|date=2020-07-15|accessdate=2020-07-16|archive-date=2021-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210104090314/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-53416277|dead-url=no}}</ref>EBC稍後宣稱報導有誤並致歉。在下游的蘇丹宣稱青尼羅河水位下降。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-53429014|title=River Nile dam: Sudan blasts 'unilateral' move as Ethiopia dam fills|publisher=BBC|date=2020-07-16|accessdate=2020-07-16|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219213339/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-53429014|dead-url=no}}</ref>2020年7月21日，埃塞俄比亞總理辦公室在聲明中確認復興大壩的第一年蓄水目標已完成。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.france24.com/en/20200721-ethiopia-says-it-has-reached-first-year-target-for-filling-divisive-mega-dam|title=Ethiopia says it has reached first-year target for filling divisive mega-dam|publisher=France 24|date=2020-07-21|accessdate=2020-07-30|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113144549/https://www.france24.com/en/20200721-ethiopia-says-it-has-reached-first-year-target-for-filling-divisive-mega-dam|dead-url=no}}</ref>2021年7月19日，西莱希·贝克莱宣佈復興大壩已完成第二年的蓄水計劃。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/7/19/ethiopia-says-second-filling-of-renaissance-dam-complete|title=Ethiopia says second filling of Renaissance Dam complete|website=aljazeera.com|date=2021-07-19|accessdate=2021-07-23|archive-date=2021-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210823052609/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/7/19/ethiopia-says-second-filling-of-renaissance-dam-complete|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2021年9月，埃塞俄比亞軍方宣稱挫敗了[[提格雷人民解放阵线|提格雷人民解放阵线]]試圖破壞復興大壩建設的計劃，埃塞俄比亞軍在戰鬥中殺死50人。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://chinese.aljazeera.net/africa/2021/9/4/埃塞俄比亚政府军挫败忠于提格雷人民解放阵线团|title=埃塞俄比亚 政府军挫败忠于提格雷人民解放阵线团体破坏复兴大坝的企图|publisher=半島電視台|date=2021-09-04|accessdate=2021-09-07|archive-date=2021-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210907103546/https://chinese.aljazeera.net/africa/2021/9/4/%E5%9F%83%E5%A1%9E%E4%BF%84%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%9A%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%86%9B%E6%8C%AB%E8%B4%A5%E5%BF%A0%E4%BA%8E%E6%8F%90%E6%A0%BC%E9%9B%B7%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E9%98%B5%E7%BA%BF%E5%9B%A2|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2021年9月，聯合國安理會通過了一項聲明，鼓勵埃及、埃塞俄比亞和蘇丹在非洲聯盟的主持下“恢復談判”，“迅速敲定”關於衣索比亞復興大壩的爭議和協議。安理會在[[突尼斯|突尼斯]]起草的聲明中明確指出，該協議應“在合理時間內對埃塞俄比亞復興大壩的填補和運作具有相互接受和約束力”。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://fr.africanews.com/2021/09/16/barrage-sur-le-nil-le-conseil-de-securite-de-l-onu-reclame-une-reprise-des-negociations/|title=Barrage sur le Nil : l'ONU réclame une reprise des négociations|publisher=Africanews|date=2021-09-16|accessdate=2021-09-16|archive-date=2022-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220414230320/https://fr.africanews.com/2021/09/16/barrage-sur-le-nil-le-conseil-de-securite-de-l-onu-reclame-une-reprise-des-negociations//|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2022年2月20日，復興大壩開始投入發電。<ref name="bbc202202">{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-60451702|title=Ethiopia starts generating power from River Nile dam|publisher=BBC|date=2022-02-20|accessdate=2022-02-21|archive-date=2022-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220324034337/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-60451702|dead-url=no}}</ref>

